网页加载", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134619}, {"id": 194579, "content": "上班路上堵车", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009923}, {"id": 194835, "content": "“正在清关”。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1010527}, {"id": 195091, "content": "等公交车，对面的站牌过去一辆又一辆", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994836}, {"id": 194581, "content": "我让男票帮着做件事的时候，他和我说“等我这盘游戏打完”???? 老娘不等！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 675282}, {"id": 211479, "content": "基本什么都不愿意等待，急性子\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038122}, {"id": 194839, "content": "等车", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721545}, {"id": 194584, "content": "等你回消息。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1006494}, {"id": 194840, "content": "等人墨迹", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 962723}, {"id": 194585, "content": "去餐厅吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 947305}, {"id": 194841, "content": "海淘的东西总要等一个月", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952576}, {"id": 201242, "content": "等他回微信", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589135}, {"id": 194586, "content": "外卖 打饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800043}, {"id": 194842, "content": "吃饭……\n不得不说在食堂排队打饭是我最煎熬的时候，外面吃饭点菜过了半小时都不上菜也很可怕……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008958}, {"id": 194587, "content": "饿了，想吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993040}, {"id": 194843, "content": "您的订单正在派送~", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1010345}, {"id": 194844, "content": "我们把这道题讲完就下课?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922475}, {"id": 194589, "content": "一些无聊的面子工程：无聊的讲座，花大把时间等那些所谓的gp领导", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002901}, {"id": 194845, "content": "到政府机关办事", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275828}, {"id": 194590, "content": "在本来就是为了节省时间的事上：坐地铁、买快餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 968051}, {"id": 194591, "content": "广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772194}, {"id": 194593, "content": "很多事情的抉擇與選擇。不想猶豫也不想琢磨太久。只想遵循第一時間的感覺做出決斷。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009939}]}